# Project: AuditLedger Documentation Site

Public-facing MkDocs documentation for the AuditLedger GitHub organization. Built with Material theme, deployed to GitHub Pages.

## Tech Stack

- MkDocs 1.5+ with Material theme 9.5+
- Python 3.11+
- GitHub Actions for CI/CD
- Deployed to GitHub Pages

## File Structure

```
docs/                   # All documentation source
  ├── index.md         # Landing page
  ├── getting-started/ # Onboarding guides
  ├── sdk/             # SDK documentation
  ├── api/             # API reference
  ├── deployment/      # Deployment guides
  ├── dashboards/      # Dashboard docs
  ├── community/       # Contributing, support, CoC
  └── assets/          # Images, diagrams
mkdocs.yml             # Site configuration & navigation
requirements.txt       # Python dependencies
start-mkdocs.sh        # Server management script
```

## Project Goals

- Developer-focused documentation
- Clear onboarding paths
- Comprehensive API/SDK references
- Deployment and integration guides
- Community contribution guidelines
